specialities:
Welcome to CARGO CABBIE®!

Let us take you on a little tour of our special services!  Cargo Cabbie provides high quality professional moving and packing services for all sizes and types of residential and commercial moves.  We also have a full-range of moving and packing supplies at our Box Shop that we can deliver straight to your door.
We help with all sizes of moves from Eight-bedroom houses to single-item deliveries (Cargo Cabbie Express).  We also provide in-home moves and on-site loading / unloading, if you are only looking to stage or rearrange your home, or move your furniture out to a pod / truck in your driveway.  We can help!  We also provide professional packing services if you would like help packing and/or unpacking your home or office.  You have the option of purchasing cardboard boxes or renting our eco-friendly plastic bins, whether we do the packing or you do.  Our crews are also skilled at furniture assembly / disassembly, if you have one or a few items you would like help with.  Whatever your moving or packing needs, we can help!

Visit our Box Shop online  We offer all sizes of boxes, bubble wrap, white newsprint, dish and glass kits, shrink wrap, tape, tape dispensers, art/mirror boxes, TV boxes and more!  If you are local to us in the downtown core of Toronto we can deliver your order free of charge.  

We look forward to hearing from you!  We're here to help!

profile:
WE  PROVIDE   FREE   ON   SITE   ESTIMATES IN THE GTA! 
 
WE PROVIDE TEMP CONTROLLED, SECURE STORAGE, ON MONTH TO MONTH BASES! CUSTOMERS THAT STORE THREE OR MORE MONTHS GET ONE MONTH FREE!!!
WE SELL BOXES, PACKING PAPER, MATTRESS BAGS, BUBBLE WRAP AND MUCH MORE! 
 
At Augusta Movers Toronto Inc., we understand the challenges when it comes to moving whether it is down the street or across the city. Moving your home or business to a new location is exciting but it can be stressful so let Augusta Movers take care of your moving needs and alleviate your anxiety. 
 
Augusta Movers offers a full range of moving, packing and storage solutions to fit your move and budget considerations including discounts for students and seniors. Our expertise in residential and commercial moving, packing and storage has earned us a solid reputation with our customers enabling our business to prosper from repeat business and referrals for local and long distance relocation. Our superior service and attention to all your moving requirements and details, makes us the best choice for your move. 
 
We are experts in what we do from smaller moves, packing and storage for apartment and condo dwellers to houses and commercial relocations of offices, stores, and restaurants. Our unique control and monitoring moving process allows our trained team of professional packers and movers to execute your move hassle-free – we guarantee it.  We believe direct communication is the key to a successful move; we will meet with you to discuss your moving requirements and provide you with a written estimate of the required services with no surprises. 
 
At Augusta Movers Toronto, we are dedicated to providing our customers with quality and fast service at competitive rates.  We are committed to consistently providing excellence in customer service unmatched and beyond industry standards; we will be there for you offering guidance and support from the beginning of your move from packing and storage to transportation of your belongings to your new location. 
 
We encourage you to browse around our site for more information on our moving, packingand storage services. To request a free estimate on your next residential and commercial move, call Augusta Movers Toronto at 416 665 9996.

profile:
Since 1992, Miracle Movers Toronto has provided thousands of satisfied customers with customized, comprehensive moving services across the GTA and Canada. Whether you're one person moving into a bachelor apartment or a midsize company moving 100 employees into a new office, our experienced, enthusiastic staff is ready to help you out.

In addition to providing basic transportation services, we can visit your home or office before the big day to plan the most efficient move possible, create a floor plan of your new destination so that you know precisely where your items will go, and even help pack - or provide boxes, padding and plastic wrap if you'd rather do so yourself. With satellite offices across Canada and partners around the world, we can then accommodate moves of any distancccommodate moves of any distance to any destination, including the USA.

At Miracle Movers Toronto, we pride ourselves on providing outstanding customer service: more than 80% of our customers are from referrals! Call us for free advice and quotations today!

profile:
Welcome to Viktoria Professional Movers – a company where customer care and satisfaction are our top priorities. 
 
There's no doubt about it, moving can be stressful!   Choosing responsible and experienced movers is one of the ways to alleviate that stress. When choosing a moving & storage company price is important, however the level of service your moving company provides you with is even more important, and often times cheap moving companies can end up costing you a fortune! Unfortunately, our industry abounds with companies whose aim to book as many jobs as they can by whatever means necessary. Many "lowball" estimates quickly balloon with unexpected charges while hurried workers provide disappointing service. For many of these companies protecting your property and ensuring your satisfaction is last on their list of priorities.
 
At Viktoria Professional Movers it's not about the number of moves, it's about the number of customers we leave happy & satisfied. Moving doesn't have to be complicated. Let us walk you through the process and get you on the way to a stress-free move to your new home. The key to a successful move is organization and we are the experts.
 
Whether you require moving, packing, or self-storage, you will never be just another client to us. Ever.

Residential and Commercial Moving and Storage, Packing and Unpacking Services.

As professional Firefighters, each day we rely on a commitment to teamwork, safety and integrity to provide our communities with emergency services when they need them most.

Applying these same principles to the Residential Moving Industry has allowed us to create a company that provides Ontario with the highest standards of moving and storage services. Why Firemen Movers? We are Safe, Dependable, Hard Working and On-time!

Our commitment to quality working practices ensures that everyone involved in your move is a trained, properly equipped and certified employee. We do not use day labor or contract out, which ensures that we can move your belongings quickly and safely. In addition to exceptionally high service levels we also support 2 important local charities, The Sick Kids Burn Unit, and the Red Door Family Shelter.

Call now to learn more about our Ontario moving services and receive a FREE, no obligation estimate for your move.

profile:
The goal at GetMovers is to provide detail-oriented moving assistance that's tailored to the needs of each customer.

That is why all GetMovers employees from call centre assistants to drivers get special trainings and their salary is highly affected by our customers satisfaction.

Our quality management system is adapting quickly to client’s needs, saving you time and money.

So, if you want to move your belongings stress-free, on time and in full safety GetMovers is the company to turn to.

We are specializing on local residential and commercial moving. Moving can be very stressful and complicated if you haven’t chosen the right moving company and completed all the preparations needed, ahead of your moving day.
You should be checking if the company have full insurance coverage for your content and the properties, full equipment including packaging materials and tools to assemble and dissemble your furniture, how many years they are in business and read their third party reviews and must have back up trucks just in case something happen on your moving date! Our Team will be happy to advice you on other things that are extremely important during your move, so call us today and will be gladly assisting you.


Moving process starts with packing.

Packing is really time consuming.

Do you know that a 2-bedroom apartment will typically take a homeowner or renter 6 hours – 1 day to pack. A two-bedroom home will likely take up to 2 days

Our trained GetMovers team is happy to free you several precious hours.

We know how to handle bulky, fragile, oddly shaped and unique items to prevent damage while transportation.
We use high quality packing supplies, containers, wardrobe boxes to ensure the smoothness of moving process.

If you prefer packing by yourself, we can deliver all necessary packing materials to your doorstep.

We also provide Partial Packing Service. It means that we would pack or unpack only large items or pack up items in a specific room.

The decision is always yours.

Get in touch and we'll Pack and unpack It for You.



Getmovers has a large operating network across Canada. So, if you. need to relocate from Toronto to Vancouver or from Edmonton to Calgary we are happy to help you.

We’re not just moving experts, we’re relocation experts. Since 2008 we constantly enriching our expertise moving people and businesses around Canada.

We have the knowledge you need for a successful relocation.

We've partnered with competent international moving companies near you to help you ship your goods to any country in the world.

You can delegate us the whole process or the most time-consuming tasks while relocation.


Get your quote on get movers.ca


Looking for secure and climate control storage space with full access to? With over 10,000 Sqft   storage capacity GetMovers provides secure solutions for short or long-term storage.

Whether you need to store furniture, commercial goods or professional equipment, our secure storage facilities across Canada are equipped with the best technology to keep your belongings safe.

Our storage facilities are regularly inspected and well equipped, we make sure your belongings are securely stored in the best conditions.

Get Movers offers both private and corporate relocation services.

A well-designed action plan of your office relocation would minimize the loss of productivity for your business.

GetMovers are well trained to pack and move your company’s assets such as office furniture and electronics to your new premises.

You probably would ask yourself after everything we covered here is why should I be choosing Get Movers? Here are only the few reasons why:
1.	All our movers are professionals and  exceptionally well trained.
2.	We use the latest technology solution to monitor live the process of your move, we know where our trucks are, crews located and their live actions (use Samsara) so while calling our customer service team will be able to answer all your questions live!
3.	Full customer service, support and management team is here to serve you 7 days a week!
4.	Back up trucks and crews in cases for last minute moves or emergencies 
5.	Exceptionally high referral rate based on our past customers that are referring us.
6.	Honest upfront pricing without any hidden fees or surprises after
7.	We are One stop shop for all your moving needs.
8.	Nationwide Canadian coverage allowing us serving you anywhere in Canada and US.
9.	Great Team with Over 12 years of successful experience in the moving industry.



So, call us now at 1888 to get your move arranged or Get your free quote on get movers.ca

Get Movers – Caring while Carrying

profile:
When we say that we move The Spirit of Your Home, we are not just using nice words, but real facts. Our company has always a complex approach to what moving means. We understand that our customers want us not to just move some stuff from one place to another, and we know that we are not just simply moving some furniture and stuffed boxes with things, but first of all, we are moving belongings with a deep spiritual value and memories for our customers. That is why it is extremely important for us to make sure that your things get safely to their destination and continue to provide your home with priceless memories.
Our priority is to make sure that all the possessions of our clients, which are filled with spiritual significance will bring the same joy throughout time, no matter how many times they are being moved to new houses, and our basic goal is to make sure that our clients remember us only from positive experience and perspective.

profile:
Hercules Moving Company Inc is a Toronto based moving company which provides high-quality household moving, commercial relocation, piano moving and storage services. 
Hercules Moving Company Inc operates in the Greater Toronto Area and offers a full moving service, including packing and unpacking services.
In addition to packing services, Hercules also offers full disassembly, and reassembly of any furniture during any move. Whether you are moving locally or simply moving a piano, Hercules Moving Company will come fully insured and bonded.
The company stands out from other moving companies Toronto, ON with its unique wrapping and packing methods which reliably protect items during the move. 
Hercules Moving Company Inc is also a long distance and cross Canada mover that provides moving services from as  far West as Vancouver Island to as far East as St. John’s, Newfoundland .

profile:
Frogbox rents reusable, industrial strength, stack-able moving boxes. We will drop off the boxes and pick them up after your move and save you and the environment the impact of using cardboard. The environmental ramification of using cardboard is significant as it makes up an estimated 18-20% of landfill material. If you are moving between cities where there are Frogbox locations you can have the Frogboxes dropped off in one city and picked up in another. Make your move easier by using Frogbox eco-friendly reusable moving boxes and other moving supplies. We have worked with all the Movers in the cities we service and can refer credible movers (and tell you who to avoid :)).  
FROGBOX was a successful contender on The Dragon's Den.

profile:
Aleks moving started in 2007 with family at the core, we are family owned and operated and we put that care we have for our own family into the care we show for our clients and their belongings. Moving can be stressful so we ensure we take the time to do a walkthrough with you, to carefully pack (if needed)  and load/unload your belongings safely and carefully.

 During these times we also work to ensure all of our staff are equipped with the proper safety gear and that our moving equipment and trucks are cleaned and sanitized prior to your move, we also offer FLAT RATE FEE and offer 24/7 care and service. We offer the best rates in Ontario. CALL US TODAY FOR A FREE ESTIMATE


• All staff are equipped and trained with safety gear, such as masks, gloves, clothing + hand sanitizer
• Aleks Moving has implemented strict and extensive cleaning and sanitizing practices for all our moving equipment like blankets and straps, and the interior and exterior of our trucks
• We are constantly monitoring each staff for symptoms and encouraging them to stay home if they are not feeling well
• One person social distancing walk through of your home prior to your move to ensure everything is clear and understood. 

Please stay safe , wash yours hands often and practice social distancing. 

Free estimates at your convenience, including coming out to your home to view what you have to move so we have a better understanding so that on the day of the move there are no surprises for you or the movers. packing and unpacking if required, protection of all furniture, dismantling and reassembling, short and long-term storage, inventory service, and many other services.

profile:
At TouchWood Movers, our mission is to make sure we are able to alleviate the moving stress off of the customer by providing top quality service without burning a hole in their pocket. We try to touch hearts with our craft, dedication and congeniality. 

WHY CHOOSE US:
 We always give written estimates whether it’s a flat price or an hourly price. All our in-house estimates are free of cost.
 We do not bring out hidden charges at the time of final payment.
 We charge reasonable prices and provide top notch service.
 All of our trucks are in mint condition and they carry all types of moving equipment.
 We are fully insured and bonded.
 We believe in growing and nurturing customer relationship.
 Last minute, short notice or advance bookings, we cater all.
 Our staff is extremely professional with an experience of more than 10 years. They know what they’re doing.

COVID UPDATE:
 We're doing our best to ensure the safety of our clients as well as our front-line crew members during this tough time:
 Our trucks are washed and sanitized periodically.
 All personal protective equipment including gloves and masks is mandatory for every crew member.
 As for the safety of our clients and crew members, we ask all our clients to avoid more than 2 people while moving and to maintain 2 m distance.

profile:
Benini Moving and Storage is a Toronto-based relocation and storage company. Our mission is to provide our clients with the highest quality of service, founded upon the principles of efficiency and reliability. We offer a wide variety of MOVING SERVICES, carefully customized to meet the needs and budget of each client.

To start off, get a FREE ESTIMATE for your move. One of our professional moving managers will contact you with your quote, and answer all your questions. We will even provide you with FREE DELIVERY of all the packing supplies you need.

With Benini, you can relax knowing that your valuables will be handled with the utmost care.
products:
WHAT WE DO

1/ We sign a contract before the job starts with the starting time indicated and the conditions were already discussed with the customer.
2/ We completely wrap the furniture with thick moving blankets to avoid any damages or scratches.
3/ We carefully pack the dishes, glasses and other fragile items with white packing paper.
4/ We take care of pictures and paintings.
5/ We load the truck in a proper way to avoid the furniture shifting and damaging during transportation.
6/We try finding creative solutions to the issues which may occur during the job.
7/ We hoist sofas and other heavy pieces through a balcony if there is no other ways to bring them in.
8/ We conduct our service in a very friendly manner.
9/We work very hard until the job is completed.
services:
WHAT WE DO NOT DO:

1/ We are never late. In fact, we always try to arrive early. 
2/ We do not have “stair” charges.
3/ We do not have ANY hidden charges.
4/ We do not prolong the job deliberately in order to make extra money.
5/ We do not keep our customers’ belongings locked in the truck as a “hostage” while negotiating to get extra payment.
6/ We do not insist to get paid in full before the job is completed.
7/ We do not insist to receive free pizza and beer for lunch.
8/ We do not insist to be tipped even if you are not pleased of our service.
payment_method: Cash, Cheque, Bank draft, E-mail money transfer, Credit Card
name: Benini Moving

Moving to another part of Toronto Gta? Undecided between handling the move all on your own or hiring a professional moving company? A wise choice would be to retain Raptor as your local mover service provider for your household move in Toronto Gta. You can be assured of a relocation experience that caters to your exact needs, budget and timelines. At Raptor Movers we understand that every household or commercial enterprise will have different needs when it comes to moving. While some folks may need help only with the heavy lifting, others may require a full-service relocation. Tell us what you need; our local mover services suit Toronto residents for their individual relocation requirements Whether you are moving from Toronto to Ottawa, just across the street, or 2 blocks away, we will make it easy for you. Our comprehensive coordination and theft handling of your move will ensure a stress-free moving experience.

Whether you’re moving a 1 bedroom apartment, or a 4 bedroom home, moving can be stressful. Let us help rid you of that stress. Being in business for 10 years, we’ve seen it all, and we’ve learned to make your move as smooth as possible, whether this is your first move, or your 10th move. Backed with our many reviews and years of experience, we strive to continue to be Toronto's favorite mover. Our clean, eco-friendly moving trucks and uniformed staff will arrive on your moving day with a smile, and help make your day a whole lot better. We shrink wrap your fragile furniture to keep them as safe as possible during your move, and pad them for extra measure. Our moving crew members are experienced trained professionals who take pride in their work. profile:
Vaultra Storage is a 100% Canadian owned and operated. The company is a one-stop storage solution, featuring self storage, pick up and delivery service, LAUFT coworking spaces and rental moving boxes. Each facility offers simple, seamless and secure storage solutions for all. Whether looking to store for business or personal use, Vaultra’s team will find the services that fit their customers best.

Vaultra self storage facilities offer convenient and secure locations, with units that range from traditional drive-up, indoor, heated, climate controlled to outdoor vehicle storage. Visit vaultrastorage.ca/self-storage to find a location nearby!

The pick up and delivery service, Vaultra Door to Door, is available throughout the GTA. It's simple: Vaultra movers pick up items and store them at a Vaultra facility. When the items are needed again, Vaultra Door to Door returns them! To see service areas, as well as the Door to Door storage plans available, visit d2d.vaultra.ca.

LAUFT coworking spaces are featured in Vaultra Storage's Toronto Castlefield and Ajax locations. Their state of the art facilities are perfect for business owners and/or entrepreneurs who want a space to work, while having their inventory right around the corner. Book a coworking space at lauft.work!

The rental moving box service, Vaultra CityBoxes, offers 27” x 17” x 12” bins that are stackable and reusable. First Vaultra CityBoxes delivers the bins. Then, clients pack, move and unpack. Afterwards, they pick up the bins! To see the service area and rent moving boxes, visit vaultrastorage.ca/bin-rental.

profile:
Vaultra Storage is a 100% Canadian owned and operated. The company is a one-stop storage solution, featuring self storage, pick up and delivery service, LAUFT coworking spaces and rental moving boxes. Each facility offers simple, seamless and secure storage solutions for all. Whether looking to store for business or personal use, Vaultra’s team will find the services that fit their customers best.

Vaultra self storage facilities offer convenient and secure locations, with units that range from traditional drive-up, indoor, heated, climate controlled to outdoor vehicle storage. Visit vaultrastorage.ca/self-storage to find a location nearby!

The pick up and delivery service, Vaultra Door to Door, is available throughout the GTA. It's simple: Vaultra movers pick up items and store them at a Vaultra facility. When the items are needed again, Vaultra Door to Door returns them! To see service areas, as well as the Door to Door storage plans available, visit d2d.vaultra.ca.

LAUFT coworking spaces are featured in Vaultra Storage's Toronto Castlefield and Ajax locations. Their state of the art facilities are perfect for business owners and/or entrepreneurs who want a space to work, while having their inventory right around the corner. Book a coworking space at lauft.work!

The rental moving box service, Vaultra CityBoxes, offers 27” x 17” x 12” bins that are stackable and reusable. First Vaultra CityBoxes delivers the bins. Then, clients pack, move and unpack. Afterwards, they pick up the bins! To see the service area and rent moving boxes, visit vaultrastorage.ca/bin-rental.

profile:
Moving & Storage

Bedwell Van Lines has been a family owned and operated firm established in 1946 and has been operating under the same management and staff since 1974.
 
Our success in providing superior moving services continues to be demonstrated by the repeat business of thousands of satisfied customers.
 
We worked very hard to achieve this since 1946 and we will keep working very hard to stay there.
 
All of our staff are full-time professionals dedicated to providing the very best in relocation service. Local moving, long distance moving, packing, crating, storage and shipping are just a few of the many services Bedwell provides. Our office and coordinating staff will provide their expertise in order to give you a safe, secure, worry-free move from start to finish.
 
The Bedwell Group routinely handles daily Corporate Relocations whether internal, external and Canada wide, for firms varying from Major Banking Facilities to School Boards and to many areas of Federal and Provincial Governments.

Benefits of Using Moving ASAP
 

The benefits of choosing a moving company should be carefully considered before hiring any. Moving can be physically and mentally stressful. We are the best movers in Burlington. Our trained professionals know exactly what they're doing and will make sure your move goes as smoothly as possible. We use our state-of-the-art equipment to ensure that there are no damages or delays on your move day.

 

Our prices are unbeatable, with movers available 7 days a week. Whether you need to be moved across town or across the country, we have got you covered.

 
What Makes Moving ASAP Different?
 

Moving is a never-ending process, and there's always something that needs to be done. Whether it's packing, organizing or hiring the best movers, there is no shortage of tasks to tackle. It can all feel like one big task and leave you feeling overwhelmed and frustrated with the entire moving process. 

 

There's no need to worry because we have your back! Here, at Moving ASAP, we make sure you're completely satisfied with your move by going above and beyond. We'll take care of the packing, organizing, and scheduling so you can just sit back and relax.

 

Why should I choose Moving ASAP?
 

Moving ASAP provides a wide selection of moving services at the most competitive prices in the business. Our friendly and professional staff will make sure that your move is stress-free with us.

Moving ASAP provides a wide selection of moving services at the most competitive prices in the business. They can handle all sorts of residential and commercial moves, including families and businesses alike.

 

Our Competitive Services
 

All of our employees are trained, highly-skilled professionals

 

Moving ASAP has been in business for over 1 year and in this time, we have developed the credentials to be one of the top movers in the city. We are also well-trained, highly-skilled professionals with extensive experience moving homes, offices, and everything in between.

profile:
To all our customers for the past 25 years, Dino’s Movers would like to express our gratitude for your business and support.

Local Moving Services:

Dino’s Movers provides the same level of care on local moving in Toronto as if moving long distance. We prepare and blanket your furniture to be moved the same way we do for long distance. 

Long Distance Moving Service:

Dino’s Movers offers two types of long distance to some locations with in Ontario Canada.

Option #1- Direct load:

Direct load is offered to some cities with in Ontario, with direct load the same services is offered as local moving. Depending on volume of move we pick up and deliver on the same day or next day.

Option #2- Van Line Service:

Van Line Service is provided for moves that are relocating across Canada or the US, this service is combine moving shipments going in the same direction. This means that your load of moving belonging are combined with other customers that are going in the same direction. 

International Moving Services:

Overseas container service is used to relocate goods to another continent. The most economical way to relocate overseas is when customer arranges for the container service to destination and have Dino’s Movers prepare and pack container. At destination customer may off load container or hire local movers to off load. 

Dino’s Movers Storage 

At our location in Toronto we offer storage units or warehouse space. We provide different sizes of storage units for self-storage customers or warehouse space for customers that need to store a few items. In addition to providing very reasonable storage prices, we don’t remove our blankets from your furniture if you use our moving service to move into our storage.   

Plastic Moving Bins Rentals:

Dino’s Movers Eco-Friendly plastic moving boxes makes the process of packing and moving faster and easier. Moving bins are easy to pack, move and stack for loading.

Moving Boxes and Supplies:

We stock different sizes of moving boxes to meet your various needs and moving supplies to help you with your packing and shipping requirements. We offer free delivery with-in Toronto (some conditions apply).

profile: When it comes to relocation, finding a reliable mover (Toronto moving services, Calgary moving services, Halifax, Regina etc.) with a trustworthy reputation is critical. Unfortunately, the advancements of the Internet have made it easy for anyone to put up a nice looking website and pose as a professional movers. Though the appearance may be professional, some of these moving services are actually unprofessional operators who may not even own a truck, or have access to proper moving equipment. To give consumers peace of mind when looking for a good movers, the Canadian Moving and Storage Network (CMSN) established their own Movers & Storage Search System which certifies that moving and storage members have not only agreed to abide by our high standards and ethics, but have also passed a thorough services background check. The CMSN's new Movers & Storage Search System makes it easy for consumers to find qualified movers by company name, mover type, province, town, postal code, and many other useful search criteria.
name: Canadian Moving And Storage Network   No Longer In Business

profile:
iMove Canada is proud to offer reliable and affordable moving services to families and businesses in and around The Greater Toronto Area, including Oakville, Mississauga, Etobicoke, Toronto, Richmond Hill and Ajax.

Local or long distance, our moving crews are available 24/7 to accommodate your moving needs. Our professional movers and a fleet of fully equipped moving trucks can handle variety of projects, from a small delivery to a 3 bedroom house, to a high-rise building.

Please call us in advance for an on-site estimate and qualify for reduced advance booking rates.

iMove Canada specializes in apartment moving, condo moving, house moving, office moving and corporate relocation. We offer local and long distance moving services with professional crews and fully equipped moving trucks. Packing supplies, packing services, long term self-storage or overnight storage, loading or unloading of PODS, hoisting of furniture, moving a piano or safe and other specialty services available. iMove Canada offers discounts for seniors, students, home staging professionals and Realtors.

profile:
When looking for a professional experienced moving company, you can count on V.K. Trans Movers. Committed to providing fast, reliable, and efficient services to consumers and businesses for both local and long distance moving. Every year V.K. Trans Movers moves thousand of satisfied customers all because here at V.K. Trans we understand that moving can be an overwhelming experience and we try to make it smooth, hassle free and pleasant.

Our team of experts will help you make this process go smooth from beginning to end. Whether it starts with a free quote over the phone, conducting a visual estimate or the final stages of delivering your furniture, you are in good and gentle hands with V.K. Trans.
Our business has grown exponentially but still offers the quality services that family businesses are known for.
